<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.9.2">
<l>māṉēy kaṇmaṭavār mayakkilpaṭ ṭumānilattu</l>
<l>nāṉē nāṉāvi tanarakampukum pāvañceytēṉ</l>
<l>tēṉēy pūmpoḻilcūḻ tiruvēṅkaṭa māmalaiye</l>
<l>ṉāṉāy vantaṭaintē ṉaṭiyēṉaiyāṭ koṇṭaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being caught in the charms of simple maids with doe-like eyes,</l>
<l>I committed every kind of hell-bound sin on [this] great earth.</l>
<l>My bull elephant of great Tiruvēṅkaṭa Mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">ringed by groves of blossoms with nectar,</l>
<l>I came [here and] took refuge; be gracious, receiving me,</l>
<l rend="indent">[your] servant, in service.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
